---
// Hero Section Component
---

<section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-blue-50 py-12 lg:py-20">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-6">
          Sales Training for Financial Professionals Who Prefer 
          <span class="text-red-600">Relationships</span> Over 
          <span class="text-gray-400 line-through">Pushy Tactics</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
          Learn the Power of Authenticity method from someone who understands your reluctance to 'sell'. 
          Transform how you approach business development without compromising your values.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Designed specifically for financial services</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Based in Exeter, serving Southwest UK</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Small group workshops (maximum 20 participants)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700">CPD points available</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">
            Enquire About Next Workshop
          </a>
          <a href="#approach" class="btn-secondary">
            Learn Our Approach
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-8">
          <img 
            src="https://www.thereluctantsalesman.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Terry3.png" 
            alt="Terry Mullins - The Reluctant Salesman"
            class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg"
          />
          <div class="mt-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Terry Mullins</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Founder, The Reluctant Salesman</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2 italic">
              "I never saw myself as a 'natural salesperson' - and that became my greatest strength"
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>